This is the license for the Alpha release of the Model Context Factory (MCF).  
By using the software ("MCF"), you agree to the following terms:

1. Permitted Use  
You may use, modify, and integrate MCF into your personal or commercial projects if your total revenue from all products or services using MCF is less than 10,000 USD per month.

2. No Resale or Repackaging  
You may not sell, license, distribute, or repackage MCF itself.  
You may not offer MCF as a competing SDK, framework, API, or toolkit.  
You may not resell or redistribute MCF in a way that competes with the original project.

3. Attribution  
If you use MCF in a commercial product, a visible acknowledgment of "Powered by the Model Context Factory (MCF)" must appear in documentation or an About section.

4. Restrictions  
You may not remove copyright notices.  
You may not claim ownership of MCF.  
You may not use MCF to train or improve any model that competes with the MCF framework.

5. Enterprise or High-Revenue Use  
If your total revenue from products using MCF reaches or exceeds 10,000 USD per month, you must obtain a commercial license. Contact the MCF team for details.

6. No Warranty  
MCF is provided "as is" without any warranties or guarantees of performance, safety, or fitness for purpose.

7. Limitation of Liability  
The authors are not liable for damages, loss of revenue, or data loss arising from the use of MCF.

8. Termination  
Violation of this license terminates your rights to use MCF.

